{"pin":"BH00050","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00050","anchor":"","first_line":"This is a Book from which the trees inhale the fragrance of springtime, and from which the sons perceive the sweet perfume of their tender, bountiful Father [3.5s]... ...The beginning of all things is the knowledge of God, and the end of all things is strict observance of whatsoever hath been sent down","first_line_orig":"هذا کتاب یجد منه الاشجار عرف الربیع و الابناء رآئحه الاب المشفق الکریم  ","language":"1","word_count":"5800","subjects":"@the Word of God; influence and centrality of, @proclamation to people of the Bayan, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God, @steadfastness; perseverance; faithfulness, @martyrs and martyrdom, @alcohol and drugs; tobacco; opium","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V1/Contents.html\"\u003eROB1.048\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#238\"\u003eLL#238\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#451\"\u003eLL#451\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_n